                <h1>Does Chipotle Conduct Background Checks for Employees?</h1>
                <p>Yes, Chipotle does conduct background checks as part of its hiring process. This ensures a safe and secure working environment by verifying the candidate's criminal history and past employment. Prospective employees should be prepared for this step when applying for a position at Chipotle.</p>
